These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, 7up
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, handball, golf
1. the person who's sport is handball is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | water | 7up   |
| Sport      | rowing    | handball  | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, lemonade
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, chinese, indian
1. the spanish is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the chinese is on the far left##1
3. the chinese is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | water     | lemonade      |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, milk
There 3 different types of food: apple, corn, watermelon
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | milk  | iced-tea       |
| Food       | apple     | corn | watermelon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, lemon, avocado
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, sudoku
1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | avocado    | lemon     | raspberry |
| Hobby   | sudoku | board-games | traveling     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, train
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the owner of the rat##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | rabbit | cat     | rat |
| Transport   | train        | snowmobile | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, mango, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, roller, subway
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person eating mango is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating pineapple is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | pineapple | avocado      | mango  |
| Transport   | scooter       | roller | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, dubstep
3 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, horse
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of country is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep      | ambient     | country    |
| Pet           | frog | horse | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
