2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person eating garlic is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pepper | pear | garlic      |
| Hobby   | chess     | fishing | sudoku |

