.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, baking, dancing
3 different pets are kept: frog, fish, chinchilla
1. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | baking | collecting  |
| Pet     | chinchilla     | frog      | fish |

