.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, time-travel, epic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | milk    | water    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | superhero | epic |

