.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, cucumber, strawberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, entrepreneur, coach
1. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
3. the firefighter is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | lettuce     | strawberry   | cucumber     |
| Job    | coach | entrepreneur | firefighter |

