3 different pets are kept: rat, goldfish, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the software-developer is on the left of the bartender##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | fisherman    | software-developer | bartender |
| Pet   | dog | rat     | goldfish        |

