.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, house, metal
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | coffee  | lemonade | hot-chocolate  |
| Music-Genre   | house | metal   | ambient |

