.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, videographer, dancer
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, dutch, canadian
1. the canadian is on the far left##1
2. the electrician is on the far right##1
3. the malaysian is the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | videographer | dancer | electrician |
| Nationality   | canadian  | malaysian      | dutch |

