The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person eating cherry is the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | pear | watermelon   | cherry        |
| Sport   | water-polo    | volleyball | sailing |

