2. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of d&b##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | baking | reading |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | d&b     | trance  |

