.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: tomato, zucchini, nectarine
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, basketball
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | nectarine | tomato       | zucchini  |
| Sport   | basketball  | rowing | badminton |

 